data.description: OPEN HOUSE CANCELED! Step into this home and immediately fall in love! This house has all the elegance and charm wrapped in brick! Over 2200 sq ft, three sizable bedrooms, with one being used as a decadent custom closet along with a full and half bath! The well sized primary bedroom features a functional marble woodburning fireplace! The main level has a large formal living room and yet again another marble wood burning fireplace! Desire a cozy spot to nestle? Hang out in the comfortably spacious family room that leads to a quaint outdoor patio! The formal dining room is perfect for hosting friends and family and the kitchen features new luxury vinyl flooring along with stainless steel appliances! Some recent updates include custom painting, tuckpointing (2022), sewer line & plumbing stack (2018), newer soffit and shutters! Located in a picturesque street in Ferguson and within walking distance of a park! Don't miss your opportunity to call this stunning house your new home!
